data.name: NON-WOVEN DRESSINGS
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- 100% Nonwoven fabric made of Viscose and Polyester Fibers
- Medical Paper
- Adhesive: Acrylic and Hotmelt

## STERILIZATION
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile

## PRESENTATIONS
- Straight and Curved Cut Transfer Paper

## PERFORMANCE
- Highly Flexible
- Skin friendly
- Hypoallergenic
- Strong hold without skin irritation (Latex-free)
